6. Canonical storage

All events are normalized before persistence.

6.1 Rules

sorted keys

normalized strings

UTC timestamps

normalized numbers

no ambiguity


6.2 Example

Input:

{
  "amount": 100.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "reference": "PAY_9f2a",
  "status": "settled"
}

Canonical:

{"amount":100,"currency":"USD","reference":"PAY_9f2a","status":"settled"}

6.3 Hash

contentHash = sha256(canonicalJson)


